{"type": "article", "id": 10552, "title": "野餐餐包", "description": "", "date": "2015-06-09T07:16:51Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 16, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235742A31Uq4blWrvYL7IT.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t来自马德里的一家设计事务所 Atelier Teratoma 将太空与野餐这两个完全不搭边的元素结合到一起，设计了这款野餐包。内含两个银色小枕头便于野餐后的小憩，支架打开就是简易餐桌，白色塑料大盒子里有扬声器、USB 充电设备、蓝牙连接的显示屏和太阳能电板。设计师说传统的野餐只是为了探索自然之美和分享食物，而在高速发展的拥挤的未来，我们以另外的方式交流，所以设计了更符合时代的餐包。<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235740a92AcX0gf8HEkU6P.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235740uXingVRFBh0Yc7Sw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235741rhOXni7yT5FxH6u1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235741DkOsgn302EoNTu6t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052357427A0Dv21jkwsKgrlP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66538462\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n"}